        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Will you believe the government of a republic, a kingdom, and an empire?\" Albert cast his eyes on the passport, then raised them in astonishment to Beauchamp.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
