        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Review your life, Albert; although it is only just beginning, did a lovely summer's day ever dawn with greater purity than has marked the commencement of your career?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
