        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Be it so,\" said Beauchamp; \"if you must have me descend to earth, I submit; and if you will seek your enemy, I will assist you, and I will engage to find him, my honor being almost as deeply interested as yours.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
