        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"'Whose name is'--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"'Danglars.'\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Make inquiries, Albert, but do not be angry without reason; make inquiries, and if it be true\"--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Oh, yes, if it be true,\" cried the young man, \"he shall pay me all I have suffered.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Act prudently.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Oh, do not fear; besides, you will accompany me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Let us go immediately.\" They sent for a cabriolet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000027_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000027_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "You appear to forget yourself sadly.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"No, sir,\" said Albert, coldly; \"there are circumstances in which one cannot, except through cowardice,--I offer you that refuge,--refuse to admit certain persons at least.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Is it my fault that your father has dishonored himself?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Yes, miserable wretch!\" cried Morcerf, \"it is your fault.\" Danglars retreated a few steps.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000034_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000034_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Have I travelled in that country?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"No; it is not you who have directly made this exposure and brought this sorrow on us, but you hypocritically provoked it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"I?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "How came it known?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"I suppose you read it in the paper in the account from Yanina?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Who wrote to Yanina?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"To Yanina?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Yes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"One only?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"I, doubtless, wrote.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"I, indeed?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Who, then, urged you to write?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Tell me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"The Count of Monte Cristo told you to write to Yanina?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"I accuse no one, sir,\" said Danglars; \"I relate, and I will repeat before the count what I have said to you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Does the count know what answer you received?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "\"Yes; I showed it to him.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000059_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000059_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "In short, why should I have any more to do with the affair?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000060_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000060_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Danglars defended himself with the baseness, but at the same time with the assurance, of a man who speaks the truth, at least in part, if not wholly-not for conscience' sake, but through fear. Besides, what was Morcerf seeking?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000060_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000060_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "And, in addition to this, everything forgotten or unperceived before presented itself now to his recollection.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000060_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000060_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Monte Cristo knew everything, as he had bought the daughter of Ali Pasha; and, knowing everything, he had advised Danglars to write to Yanina.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000060_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000060_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Lastly, he had taken Albert to Normandy when he knew the final blow was near.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_121106_000060_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/121106/1241_121106_000060_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Albert took Beauchamp aside, and communicated these ideas to him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_137614_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/137614/1241_137614_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "CHAPTER twelve.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_137614_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/137614/1241_137614_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
        "content": "Also I beseech your good grace that I may take my leave at my lady, your daughter, and at all the barons and knights.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1241_137614_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1241/137614/1241_137614_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1241",
